creator: Tadpul Tech
descriptionHtml:
Xplorro is a 3D science, strategy and exploration game. It aims to nurture future science and tech leaders by making science super fun and intuitive for young children.

Xplorro teaches educational concepts through gameplay. It also develops business and time management skills.

The overall mission is to get as many Rho (currency) as possible. You gain Rho by collecting and selling resources (If you are unable to sell any item by the end of the game, you will still receive scrap value for those items – but you gain way more if you sell items during the game).

The game has 3 levels:

1. Tutorial – Minor quest to gain an understanding of the controls
2. Mission – Magnetism quest
3. Resource Hunt – 15 min quest where player has to collect as many resources and return to the pod before the time interval ends

The game is deemed complete when you complete all three levels
descriptionShort: Help humanity discover a new habitat using science
title: Xplorro - 3D Science Game for Ages 7 to 13

creator: Tadpul Tech
descriptionHtml:
XPLORRO is a game-based science learning metaverse.

Xplorro’s survival missions require you to learn and use science concepts in the newly discovered exoplanet Eridu.

“Enjoy the fun learning experience with XPLORRO.”

Xplorro is a delightful mix of trending distance learning and ever-evolving skill-building. Let your child have the most efficient screen time by indulging in an innovative gaming experience.

With the advancement of technology and the leap of imparting education in disciplines, the developers have created this safe-space experiment lab for experiencing a wholesome understanding of how the world works.

XPLORRO-INSIDE THE GAME: HOW DOES IT WORK?

How to begin:
- The game installs on your device and is ready to use
- Sign up with XPLORRO
- Set up your Avatar
- Watch Melissa nurture the future players and explore Eridu.

Melissa is missing!
- The storyline of the game is created to suit the needs of sequential learning
- The plots and twists along the way help your child push the boundaries of imagination and scientific possibilities
- Sustainable and eco-friendly missions help your child evolve in problem-solving and decision-making suited to address 21st-century social issues
- Addresses the curiosity of invention through the CRAFT MENU which plays an integral role in learning science with XPLORRO

What to expect?
- If you are looking for 21st-century skills to survive a fast-changing world, join us on XPLORRO
- Provides a conceptual and engaging understanding of science concepts
- Assesses the learning through in-built quizzes
- Incentives and rewards on completion of missions
- Survival skills, financial planning, healthy living, management and comprehension skills are reinforced along the way in the game
descriptionShort: Help humanity discover a new habitat using science
title: Xplorro: Metaverse of Learning
